🐦 Assignment: Extend the PetAdoptionCenter with a Bird Class
Part 1 – Create the Bird Class
Requirements:
Create a new class called Bird. The class must inherit from Pet
Add a new private attribute:
    double wingSpan
Create:
A constructor
Getter and setter methods
Override the toString() method
    The toString() method should print:
        Name
        Wing span
A bird sound (for example: "chirp chirp!")

Part 2 – Modify the PetAdoptionCenter
You must update the program so that:
The user can type "bird" when registering a pet
The program asks:
    Enter wing span in meters:
A Bird object is created and stored in the Pet[] array

Part 3 – Validation
Make sure:
Wing span must be greater than 0
If the user enters invalid input, show a message and ask again.
A message could be: "Invalid number!"